Privacy Policy for Tasbih Counter

Effective Date: 4th October 2023

Introduction

Welcome to Tasbih Counter, the electric vehicle charging station finder app. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use the Tasbih Counter.

Information We Collect

1. Location Information: We collect your device’s location information to provide you with nearby electric vehicle charging stations.
2. User-Provided Information: We may collect information you provide when you use our app, such as your preferences, charging station reviews, and feedback.
3. Log Data: Our servers may automatically record information when you use the app, including IP addresses, app usage, and device information.

How We Use Your Information

1. To Provide Services: We use your location information to help you find and navigate to nearby electric vehicle charging stations.
2. Communication: We may use your contact information to send you notifications, updates, and service-related information.
3. Improvement: We analyze user data to improve our app’s functionality, content, and user experience.

Sharing Your Information

We may share your information in the following circumstances:

1. With Service Providers: We may share data with third-party service providers that help us deliver our services.
2. Legal Requirements: We may disclose information if required by law or to protect our rights, privacy, safety, or property.

Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your data, but no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure.

Your Choices

You can control how we collect and use your information by adjusting app settings. You may also choose not to provide certain information, although this may limit your ability to use certain features of the app.

Children’s Privacy

Tasbih Counter is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.


Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at usamaashraf@gmail.com

By using the Tasbih Counter, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
